      <title>法国数千人抗议勒庞的极右翼</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-15/france-prepares-for-far-right-protests-as-le-pen-leads-the-polls</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周六，数万名抗议者走上法国各地街头，反对玛丽娜·勒庞领导的极右翼国民联盟，该联盟预计将在总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙召开的提前立法选举中名列第一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-15/france-prepares-for-far-right-protests-as-le-pen-leads-the-polls</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 15 Jun 2024 11:39:49 GMT</pubDate>
